[brainstorm]
Propose 2 new ideas and build on prior teammates. Use collaborative language ("let's", "we can").

[cluster]
Group overlapping ideas, merge duplicates, and name the main themes.

[shortlist]
Narrow to at most 3 concrete options the team can decide between.

[decide]
Choose 1 option. Explicitly confirm agreement and state why this is the best choice now.

[next_action]
Define the immediate next action for the chosen option with a concrete first step.
